{"pageProps":{"postData":{"id":"deploying-github-blog","contentHtml":"<ol>\n<li>\n<p>Create a github repository with the same name as your account name.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Clone the repository and initialise with a nextjs blog starter</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"hl hl-bash\"><div class=\"hl-header\"><div class=\"hl-language\"><span>bash</span></div></div><pre id=\"MC45MTIyMDc0\" style=\"--hl-line-number-gutter-factor: 1\"><code tabindex=\"0\"><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\">1</span>npx create-next-app@latest nextjs-blog \\</span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\">2</span>--use-npm \\</span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\">3</span>--example <span class=\"pl-s\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span>https://github.com/vercel/next-learn/tree/main/basics/dynamic-routes-starter<span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span></span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>Install and confgiure gh-pages</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"hl hl-bash\"><div class=\"hl-header\"><div class=\"hl-language\"><span>bash</span></div></div><pre id=\"MC44NzkxMDA0\"><code tabindex=\"0\"><span class=\"line\">npm install gh-pages</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<ol start=\"4\">\n<li>Configure the next.config.js file, replace <code>&#x3C;repo_name></code></li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"hl hl-js\"><div class=\"hl-header\"><div class=\"hl-language\"><span>js</span></div></div><pre id=\"MC42MzAyNDg4\" style=\"--hl-line-number-gutter-factor: 1\"><code tabindex=\"0\"><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\">1</span><span class=\"pl-k\">const</span> <span class=\"pl-c1\">nextConfig</span> <span class=\"pl-k\">=</span> {</span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\">2</span>    images<span class=\"pl-k\">:</span> { unoptimized<span class=\"pl-k\">:</span> <span class=\"pl-c1\">true</span> },</span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\">3</span>    basePath<span class=\"pl-k\">:</span> isProd <span class=\"pl-k\">?</span> <span class=\"pl-s\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span>/&#x3C;repo_name><span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"pl-k\">:</span> <span class=\"pl-s\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">\"\"</span></span>,</span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\">4</span>    assetPrefix<span class=\"pl-k\">:</span> isProd <span class=\"pl-k\">?</span> <span class=\"pl-s\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span>/&#x3C;repo_name>/<span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"pl-k\">:</span> <span class=\"pl-s\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">\"\"</span></span>,</span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\">5</span>    output<span class=\"pl-k\">:</span> <span class=\"pl-s\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">'</span>export<span class=\"pl-pds\">'</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\">6</span>};</span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\">7</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\">8</span><span class=\"pl-c1\">module</span>.<span class=\"pl-smi\">exports</span> <span class=\"pl-k\">=</span> nextConfig;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<ol start=\"5\">\n<li>Run deploy!</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"hl hl-bash\"><div class=\"hl-header\"><div class=\"hl-language\"><span>bash</span></div></div><pre id=\"MC41NTA1Mjk5\"><code tabindex=\"0\"><span class=\"line\">npm run build <span class=\"pl-k\">&#x26;&#x26;</span> gh-pages -d out --nojekyll</span>\n</code></pre></div>","title":"Deploying a github blog with nextjs","date":"2025-01-15","tags":["tinkering","snippets","engineering"]}},"__N_SSG":true}